                    It would help in preserving and spreading the traditional dishes of our country which are just as important as our cultures.The website designed and developed by Team Druk Food recipes and is hosted or deployed in the heroku server and users will be given access to view, post, delete, update and comment on the post.

                </p></div>
            <div class="col150">
                <div class="imgBx">
                    <img src="images/image-1.jpg" alt="">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="testimonial" id="testimonial">
        <div class="title white">
            <div class="titletxt">The<span>W</span>ebsite looks for</div>
            <p>We are here to share love via food, and we have set goals and missions to do so.  </p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <div class="box">
                <div class="imgBx">
                    <img src="images/aim.jpg" alt="">
                    <br><br>
                </div>
                <div class="text">
                    <h3>Aim</h3>
                    <p>These interested folks can upload their recipes together with photographs and instructions on the website Druk Food Recipe. 

                        The aim of this website is to provide a user-friendly, low-cost website for those who want to share their passion of cooking by providing the essential recipes and a blog.
                        It would aid in maintaining and disseminating our nation's traditional foods, which are equally as significant to our civilizations.  
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="box">
                <div class="imgBx">
                    <img src="images/goal.webp" alt="">
                </div>
